headline: The Hartford Announces Outstanding Results For The Fourth Quarter and Full Year 2024
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., January 30, 2025--The Hartford (NYSE: HIG) today announced financial results for the fourth quarter and year ended Dec. 31, 2024.
